        "old_string": "# Camel FIX Component Implementation\n\n## Files Examined\n\n- `/workspace/components/camel-direct/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/direct/*.java` \u2014 Simple component pattern reference\n- `/workspace/components/camel-quickfix/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/quickfixj/*.java` \u2014 Complex FIX component reference\n- `/workspace/components/camel-kafka/pom.xml` \u2014 Standard component POM template\n- `/workspace/components/pom.xml` \u2014 Component registry file\n- `/workspace/components/camel-direct/src/generated/resources/META-INF/services/*` \u2014 Service descriptor patterns\n\n## Dependency Chain\n\n1. **Define configuration**: `FixConfiguration.java` \u2014 POJO with `@UriParams` and `@UriParam` annotations\n2. **Define constants**: `FixConstants.java` \u2014 Header constants for FIX message attributes\n3. **Define component**: `FixComponent.java` \u2014 Extends `DefaultComponent`, creates `FixEndpoint` instances\n4. **Define endpoint**: `FixEndpoint.java` \u2014 Extends `DefaultEndpoint`, creates Consumer and Producer\n5. **Define consumer**: `FixConsumer.java` \u2014 Extends `DefaultConsumer`, receives inbound FIX messages\n6. **Define producer**: `FixProducer.java` \u2014 Extends `DefaultAsyncProducer`, sends outbound FIX messages\n7. **Build integration**: `pom.xml` \u2014 Maven POM for the module\n8. **Component registration**: `components/pom.xml` \u2014 Register module in components list\n9. **Service descriptors**: Service descriptor files for component discovery",
        "new_string": "# Camel FIX Component Implementation - Final Report\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nSuccessfully implemented a new `camel-fix` component for Apache Camel that enables routing FIX (Financial Information eXchange) protocol messages through Camel routes. The component follows Apache Camel's standard component architecture and integrates seamlessly with the existing build system.\n\n**Compilation Status:** \u2705 SUCCESSFUL\n**All Classes Compiled:** 6 Java classes\n**Service Descriptors:** \u2705 Configured\n**Module Registration:** \u2705 Registered in components/pom.xml\n\n## Files Examined\n\n- `/workspace/components/camel-direct/` \u2014 Simple, reference component pattern\n- `/workspace/components/camel-quickfix/` \u2014 Complex FIX-related component reference\n- `/workspace/components/camel-kafka/pom.xml` \u2014 Standard component POM template\n- `/workspace/components/pom.xml` \u2014 Component module registry\n- `/workspace/components/camel-direct/src/generated/resources/META-INF/services/` \u2014 Service descriptor patterns\n\n## Dependency Chain\n\n1. **Configuration Layer**: `FixConfiguration.java` \u2014 POJO with `@UriParams` for configurable parameters\n2. **Constants Layer**: `FixConstants.java` \u2014 Header constants for FIX message metadata\n3. **Component Layer**: `FixComponent.java` \u2014 Entry point, extends `DefaultComponent`\n4. **Endpoint Layer**: `FixEndpoint.java` \u2014 Session representation, extends `DefaultEndpoint`\n5. **Consumer Layer**: `FixConsumer.java` \u2014 Inbound message handler, extends `DefaultConsumer`\n6. **Producer Layer**: `FixProducer.java` \u2014 Outbound message handler, extends `DefaultAsyncProducer`\n7. **Build Layer**: `pom.xml` \u2014 Maven project configuration\n8. **Integration Layer**: `components/pom.xml` \u2014 Module registration\n9. **Discovery Layer**: Service descriptor files for automatic component loading",
